sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Discord
    participant Listener as InteractionEventListener
    participant Manager as InteractionManagerImpl
    participant Builtin as Built-in Slash Commands
    participant Plugin as Plugin Slash Commands
    participant Other as Modal/Button/Menu

    User->>Discord: /command [options]
    Discord->>Listener: SlashCommandInteractionEvent
    Listener->>Manager: Route Interaction

    alt Slash Command
        Manager->>Manager: Find Handler by Command Name
        alt Built-in Command
            Manager->>Builtin: /settings, /ai, /channel, /command
            Builtin-->>User: Ephemeral Reply
        else Plugin Command
            Manager->>Plugin: Plugin-registered command
            Plugin-->>User: Reply
        end
    else Button/Modal/SelectMenu
        Manager->>Other: Handle Component Interaction
        Other-->>User: Reply/Update
    end
